model.product

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.common.Model
      • model.product.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IModel

    public class Product
extends Model
    The Product class encapsulates all the funtions and data associated with a "Product". It extends the Model class which contains getters and setters for the various datas.
